          "tz": -240
        },
        "subject": "LU-13643 flr: store per-mirror errors in cl_sub_dio_end",
        "message": "LU-13643 flr: store per-mirror errors in cl_sub_dio_end\n\nStore negative return codes (errors) in the mirror-specific error\narray when sub-DIO operations complete, but only if the current\nslot value is 0 (no previous error stored).\n\nThis enables FLR immediate mirror writes to track per-mirror\nI/O results for better error handling and mirror management.\n\nThese errors will be communicated to the server in the LVB for\nthe AW lock.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <pfarrell@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I25532a59f1dce99e879bab7fd20065935e931601\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
